ass=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zum1665703230237.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zum1665703230237.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zum1665703230237.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zum1665703230237\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"zum1665703230237__topic_d140852e1_d140853e1_d140854e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zum1665703230237__p_d140855e1_d140856e1_d140857e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LANGUAGE</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">Language</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zum1665703230237__section_zwj_vvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865912e65\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zum1665703230237__table_d17042e1_d17043e1_d17044e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zum1665703230237__section_u5n_vvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865912e111\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zum1665703230237__p_d140864e1_d140865e1_d140866e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$LANGUAGE</span> defines the language that\n        is to be used for the application session. This determines the language setup used. In\n        addition, the language selected, along with the library selected, affects the global\n        messages, help texts, menu bar, menus, and glyphs that are used.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zum1665703230237__p_d140867e1_d140868e1_d140869e1\">You can use the ProcScript function\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$language</span> to test or to set the current language.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zum1665703230237__section_f4g_yvx_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d865912e128\">Example: $LANGUAGE</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"zum1665703230237__pre_wnl_zvx_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; set language to French\n$LANGUAGE = FRA</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cqe1665702873537.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Language Setups</a><p>A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdn1665703008210.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$language</a><p>Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534622\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534622\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$LANGUAGE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify the language to use for global objects and language setups. $LANGUAGE { = } Language Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description $LANGUAGE defines the language that is to be used for the application session. This determines the language setup used. In addition, the language selected, along with the library selected, affects the global messages, help texts, menu bar, menus, and glyphs that are used. You can use the ProcScript function $language to test or to set the current language. Example: $LANGUAGE ; set language to French $LANGUAGE = FRA Copy Related Links Language Setups A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application. $language Return or set the current language code used for language-related global objects and language setups. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}